You'll need to install node and npm
- I got it from their website and added it to bin path

You'll also need express.
- npm install express

If you get error messages about audio format, I think firefox specific
- sudo apt install gstreamer1.0-plugins-bad

Running it locally, you'll need to change the database credentials to yours
- look at first couple lines in Server.js

To get everything running you'll need to start a server first
- node Server.js

Then the client
- firefox Mystery.html
